	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64677634"><p>If you bought the software, it's yours and you have a right to expect it to run exactly as provided in perpetuity (assuming you can provide an appropriate runtime environment).  If you have a license - well, you still have our permission to use the game service, but it's not there anymore.  Too bad, so sad, you lose.
</p><p>Straight from the pinball machine back glass:  <i>Game over, try again.</i></p></div>
